reviewText: It is a well produced instructional video and is well worth $10  but not more. look at you tube, you'll get same thing
Informative, steady progression throughout the DVD and the zooming in on actions being carried out is very good. Well worth purchasing.
This product shows you clearly and concisely how to do the most important repairs and maintenance on any bicycle- mountain or road bike.  All necessary tools for each repair are discussed as well.
